CHAMP-DEFIANCE.description:
Gain [gold]Block[/gold] equal to your [gold]Counter[/gold].
Lose all of your [gold]Counter[/gold].{InCombat:cond:
(Gain {CalculatedBlock:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold])|}

CHAMP-PREEMPTIVE_STRIKE.description:
Deal damage equal to your [gold]Counter[/gold] to ALL enemies. 
If not in [gold]Defensive[/gold], lose half of your [gold]Counter[/gold].{InCombat:cond:
(Deal {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage)|}

CHAMP-SHIELD_THROW.description:
Deal damage equal to your [gold]Block[/gold] twice.
If not in [gold]Defensive[/gold], don't gain [gold]Block[/gold] from cards next turn.{InCombat:cond:
(Deal {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage twice)|}
